OL,7,Fmembers have begun voting for the
OL,8,Fcandidate they want to succeed Mark
OL,9,FDrakeford as the party's leader and
OL,10,Fthe next first minister of Wales.
OL,12,F, the current Minister for Education
OL,13,Fand the Welsh language, and , the
OL,14,FMinister for the Economy, are both
OL,15,Fvying to be in post with a result
OL,16,Fexpected in mid-March.
OL,18,FMark Drakeford, who has been first
OL,19,Fminister since 2018, announced his
OL,20,Fintention to resign late last year.
