OL,5,Cleader
OL,7,FWhoever is successful will become the
OL,8,Ffifth leader of the country since the
OL,9,FSenedd was established in 1999.
OL,11,FMost people in Wales will not get a
OL,12,Fsay in who will be the next first
OL,13,Fminister.
OL,15,FOnly members or people part of an
OL,16,Faffiliated organisation, such as a
OL,17,Ftrade union, can participate, meaning
OL,18,Fabout 100,000 people will have a vote.
