OL,7,FUnlike previous Labour leadership
OL,8,Felections, all the votes are equally
OL,9,Fweighted.
OL,11,FJeremy Miles is supported by the
OL,12,Fmajority of Senedd Members.
OL,14,FMr Gething has the backing of most of
OL,15,Fthe large unions, and Lord Kinnock,
OL,16,Fwho led the UK Labour party from 1983
OL,17,Fto 1992.
