OL,7,FSelection in the past has used an
OL,8,F"electoral college" system, giving
OL,9,Fgreater weight to MPs and Members of
OL,10,Fthe Senedd.
OL,12,FVoting opened today (February 16) and
OL,13,Fthe result will be declared on March
OL,14,F16.
OL,16,Fis not expected to stand down
OL,17,Fimmediately and his final first
OL,18,Fminister's questions is expected on
OL,19,FMarch 19.
